@startuml
!include ../style.puml

participant "Client\nreadAt(100)" as Client
participant "Logical KV Store\n(Key: 'Account1')" as Store

note over Store
  **Logical Version Chain**
  [Account1 @ 110] -> Value: "$200"
  [Account1 @ 90]  -> Value: "$150"
  [Account1 @ 50]  -> Value: "$100"
end note

Client -> Store: read(key="Account1", readTs=100)
note right of Store
  Search for newest version 
  where timestamp <= 100
  
  110 <= 100 ? (No)
  90  <= 100 ? (Yes!) -> Return "$150"
end note

Store --> Client: "$150"
@enduml
